src:
Nina Stojanović ponovo u Top 100
04 Nov 2019, 10:51 by Darko
Srpska teniserka Nina Stojanović vratila se među prvih 100 na danas objavljenoj WTA listi.
Stojanovićeva je napredovala 15 mesta i sada je 86. teniserka sveta. Jedina je srpska predstavnica među 100 najboljih.
Napredak su ostvarile i Ivana Jorović, Aleksandra Krunić, Natalija Kostić i Olga Danilović. Jorovićeva je sada 106, Krunićeva 165, Kostićeva 168, dok je Olga Danilović na 187. mestu na WTA listi.
Ešli Barti je najbolje rangirana teniserka na kraju godine, ispred Karoline Pliškove, Naomi Osake, Simone Halep i Bjanke Andresku.

POVEZANE OBJAVE
text:
Nina Stojanovic in the Top 100 again
04 Nov 2019, 09:51 by Darko
Serbian tennis player Nina Stojanovic is back in the top 100 on today's WTA list.
Stojanovic has advanced 15 places and is now the 86th tennis player in the world. She is the only Serbian representative among the top 100.
Progress has also been made by Ivana Jorovic, Aleksandra Krunic, Natalija Kostic and Olga Danilovic. Jorovic's is now 106, Krunic's 165, Kostic’s 168, while Olga Danilovic is 187th on the WTA list.
Ashley Barty is the best-ranked tennis player at the end of the year, ahead of Carolina Plishkova, Naomi Osaka, Simone Halep and Bianca Andreska.
